=====================
Xerces-C Build Notes
=====================

Home: http://xerces.apache.org/index.html

Download: http://mirror.olnevhost.net/pub/apache/xerces/c/sources/
	  xerces-c-src_2_8_0.tar.gz

License: Apache

Build: http://xerces.apache.org/xerces-c/build-winunix.html

Uses Autoconf with custom runConfigure wrapper.
No Automake, no vpath build.

export XERCESCROOT=/path/to/xerces-c-src_2_8_0
./runConfigure -p linux -P <prefix>
make
make install

